  "description": "A ground-level view of a dry, rocky landscape. The surface is covered in a multitude of small to medium-sized rocks and pebbles, predominantly in shades of gray, brown, and reddish-tan. Scattered throughout are sparse, dried plant stalks that appear brittle and twig-like. There are also a few small, round, shrub-like plants with tight, clustered growth, suggesting they are adapted to arid conditions. The ground itself is a light, sandy color. The scene evokes a sense of desolation and a harsh environment.",
